<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Mini CTF Web</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;600;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body{
      margin:0;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg,#fafafa 0%,#f0f0f0 50%,#ffffff 100%);
      color:#333333;
      font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;
      min-height:100vh;
    }
    .ctf-wrap{
      max-width:920px;
      margin:0 auto;
      padding:40px 20px;
    }
    h1{
      color:#b8860b;
      font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;
      font-weight:700;
      font-size:2.8em;
      margin:0 0 16px;
      text-shadow:0 2px 10px rgba(184,134,11,0.2);
    }
    h2{
      color:#8b6914;
      font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;
      font-weight:600;
      font-size:1.6em;
      margin:0 0 12px;
    }
    p{
      color:#666666;
      font-size:1.1em;
      line-height:1.6;
      margin:0 0 16px;
    }
    a{
      color:#b8860b;
      text-decoration:none;
      font-weight:500;
      transition:color 0.3s ease;
    }
    a:hover{
      color:#8b6914;
      text-decoration:underline;
    }
    .card{
      background:linear-gradient(145deg,#ffffff,#f8f8f8);
      border:1px solid rgba(184,134,11,0.2);
      border-radius:12px;
      padding:24px;
      margin-top:24px;
      box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      transition:transform 0.2s ease,box-shadow 0.2s ease;
    }
    .card:hover{
      transform:translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow:0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
    }
    .back-link{
      display:inline-block;
      margin-top:32px;
      padding:12px 24px;
      background:linear-gradient(145deg,#b8860b,#8b6914);
      color:#ffffff;
      border-radius:8px;
      text-decoration:none;
      font-weight:600;
      transition:all 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow:0 4px 15px rgba(184,134,11,0.3);
    }
    .back-link:hover{
      transform:translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow:0 6px 20px rgba(184,134,11,0.4);
      color:#ffffff;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="ctf-wrap">
    <h1>Mini CTF Web</h1>
    <p>Bienvenue dans un mini défi CTF. Objectif: découvrir le flag en interagissant avec une petite application.</p>
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Défi #1 – Auth simple</h2>
      <p>Essayez de vous connecter (indices dans le code HTML/JS) et récupérez le flag.</p>
      <p><a href="#" onclick="alert('Prochainement: mini app CTF.');return false;">Lancer le défi</a></p>
    </div>
    <a href="/" class="back-link">← Retour au terminal</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
